\mt2 This book contains the account of Hosea telling about the Israeli people rejecting God, and foretelling about God punishing and restoring them. We call this book
\mt1 Hosea
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 \add I am\add* \w Hosea|strong="H1954"\w*, \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Beeri. \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w* \w these|strong="H3117"\w* \w messages|strong="H1697"\w* \add at various times\add* \w during|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w years|strong="H3117"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w Uzziah|strong="H5818"\w*, \w Jotham|strong="H3147"\w*, Ahaz, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Hezekiah|strong="H2396"\w* \w were|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w kings|strong="H4428"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Jeroboam|strong="H3379"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Jehoash \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w*.
\s1 Hosea’s wife and children
\p 
\v 2 \w When|strong="H3588"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w first|strong="H8462"\w* \add began to\add* \w give|strong="H1696"\w* messages \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w* \add to tell to the people of Israel\add*, \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w*, “\w Go|strong="H3212"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w prostitute|strong="H2181"\w*. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \add some of\add* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* \w children|strong="H3206"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* born \w as|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* result \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* \w having|strong="H3588"\w* sex \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w men|strong="H3206"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w whom|strong="H3588"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H1696"\w* \w married|strong="H3947"\w*. \w That|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* illustrate \w how|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w people|strong="H1696"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Israel \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w turned|strong="H3068"\w* \w away|strong="H3947"\w* \w from|strong="H3947"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* worship ◄idols/other gods►.”
\v 3 \w So|strong="H3947"\w* \w I|strong="H1121"\w* \w married|strong="H3947"\w* \w Gomer|strong="H1586"\w*, \w the|strong="H3947"\w* \w daughter|strong="H1323"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Diblaim|strong="H1691"\w*. She \w became|strong="H3205"\w* \w pregnant|strong="H2029"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w gave|strong="H3205"\w* \w birth|strong="H3205"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w*.
\p 
\v 4 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*, “Give \w him|strong="H7121"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w name|strong="H8034"\w* \w Jezreel|strong="H3157"\w*, \add which means ‘God scatters’\add*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w soon|strong="H4592"\w* \w punish|strong="H6485"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* descendants [MTY] \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \add King\add* \w Jehu|strong="H3058"\w* \add by scattering them\add*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* killed many \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jezreel|strong="H3157"\w* \add town\add*. \add Some day\add* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w end|strong="H7673"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w kingdom|strong="H4468"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w*,
\v 5 \w by|strong="H3117"\w* destroying \w the|strong="H3117"\w* \w power|strong="H3478"\w* [MTY] \w of|strong="H3117"\w* \add the army of\add* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w Jezreel|strong="H3157"\w* \w Valley|strong="H6010"\w*.”
\p 
\v 6 \add Later\add* Gomer \w became|strong="H3205"\w* \w pregnant|strong="H2029"\w* \add again\add*, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w she|strong="H3588"\w* \w gave|strong="H3205"\w* \w birth|strong="H3205"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w daughter|strong="H1323"\w*. \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w me|strong="H7121"\w* “\w Give|strong="H3205"\w* \w her|strong="H5375"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w name|strong="H8034"\w* \w Lo-ruhamah|strong="H3819"\w*, \add which means ‘not loved\add*,’ \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* \w longer|strong="H5750"\w* \add show that I\add* \w love|strong="H7355"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* [\w MET|strong="H5375"\w*] \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w*, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w forgive|strong="H5375"\w* \w them|strong="H7121"\w* \add for the sins that they have committed\add*.
\v 7 \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \add show that I\add* \w love|strong="H7355"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* [MTY] \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \add by saving them from their enemies\add*. However, \w it|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* \w by|strong="H3068"\w* \w weapons|strong="H2719"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w armies|strong="H3808"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w horses|strong="H5483"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* chariots \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w save|strong="H3467"\w* \w them|strong="H7355"\w*. \w Instead|strong="H3808"\w*, \w it|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* \w by|strong="H3068"\w* \add the power that I\add*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \add have\add*.”
\p 
\v 8 After Gomer \w had|strong="H3205"\w* ◄\w weaned|strong="H1580"\w*/stopped breast-feeding► \w Lo-ruhamah|strong="H3819"\w*, she \w became|strong="H3205"\w* \w pregnant|strong="H2029"\w* \w again|strong="H2029"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* she \w gave|strong="H3205"\w* \w birth|strong="H3205"\w* \w to|strong="H3205"\w* another \w son|strong="H1121"\w*.
\v 9 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w* “\w Give|strong="H1961"\w* \w him|strong="H7121"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w name|strong="H8034"\w* \w Lo-ammi|strong="H3818"\w*, \add which means 'not my people',\add* \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w of|strong="H8034"\w* \w Israel|strong="H5971"\w* \w are|strong="H5971"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* \add longer my people\add*, \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w am|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w their|strong="H3588"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w*.
\p 
\v 10 But \add some day\add* the people of Israel will be \add as numerous\add* as [SIM] the \add grains of\add* sand on the seashore; no one will be able to count them. Now \add I\add* am saying to them, ‘You are not my people,’ but then people will say to them, ‘\add You are the\add* children of God who is all-powerful.’
\v 11 \add At that time\add*, the people of Judah and the people of Israel will unite. They will appoint one leader for all of them, and they will return from the countries \add to which they have been ◄exiled/forced to go►\add*. That will be \w a|strong="H3068"\w* great time; Jezreel \add also means ‘God plants’, and it will be as though God will plant them in this country again\add*.”
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 \add At that time,\add* \w you|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w say|strong="H3478"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w your|strong="H3808"\w* fellow-Israeli \w men|strong="H1121"\w*, “\add You are\add* \w God|strong="H3808"\w*’s \w people|strong="H5971"\w*,” \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \add you will say\add* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w your|strong="H3808"\w* fellow-Israeli \w women|strong="H1992"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3808"\w* \w are|strong="H1992"\w* \w ones|strong="H1121"\w* \w whom|strong="H1992"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* loves.”
\s1 Israel will be punished and later restored
\q1 
\v 2 \add Yahweh also said to me\add*, “\w I|strong="H3588"\w* want \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w accuse|strong="H7760"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1121"\w*.
